K8s Commands

kubectl get pods												-
kubectl get services											-
kubectl describe deploy 										- To display the resources on default namespace.
kubectl get ns 													- To get all the namespaces.
kubectl create ns name_of_the_namespace 						- To create a new namespace.
kubectl apply -f filename.yaml 									- 
kubectl apply -f filename.yaml -n name_of_the_namespace			-
kubectl get deploy -n name_of_the_namespace						-
kubectl get pod -n name_of_the_namespace							-
kubectl describe pod name_of_the_pod -n name_of_the_namespace 	- To get the logs of the pod.
kubectl get sv -n name_of_the_namespace							- To get the service info which is running or not.